<section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>The <code>&lt;footnotes-wc&gt;</code> component works with <code>&lt;foot-note&gt;</code> elements to create accessible footnotes. Without JavaScript, footnotes appear inline. With JavaScript, they become superscript links with a collected list at the bottom.</p>

