  <section>
    <h2>Progressive Enhancement</h2>
    <p>The footnotes component demonstrates progressive enhancement principles.</p>

    <h3>Without JavaScript</h3>
    <p>When JavaScript is disabled or fails to load, footnotes remain inline within parentheses, keeping the content readable:</p>

    <code-block language="html" show-lines label="Rendered output without JavaScript">{{ withoutJsCode | safe }}</code-block>

    <h3>With JavaScript</h3>
    <p>When JavaScript loads, the component:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Finds all <code>&lt;foot-note&gt;</code> elements before the <code>&lt;footnotes-wc&gt;</code></li>
      <li>Converts them to superscript numbered links</li>
      <li>Collects footnote content into an ordered list</li>
      <li>Adds back-reference links from each footnote</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

