  <section>
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p>The component processes footnotes in the following steps:</p>

    <ol>
      <li><strong>Collection:</strong> Finds all <code>&lt;foot-note&gt;</code> elements that appear before the <code>&lt;footnotes-wc&gt;</code> element in document order.</li>
      <li><strong>Enhancement:</strong> Each <code>&lt;foot-note&gt;</code> gets:
        <ul>
          <li>A unique ID (e.g., <code>fnref-1</code>)</li>
          <li>A <code>data-enhanced</code> attribute</li>
          <li>The original content wrapped in a span</li>
          <li>A superscript link to the footnote</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><strong>List Generation:</strong> An ordered list is created inside <code>&lt;footnotes-wc&gt;</code> with:
        <ul>
          <li>Each footnote's content</li>
          <li>A back-reference link to the original location</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ol>

